<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <title></title>
    <style type="text/css">
			body{
				height: 97%;
				width: 99%;
				background-color: rgba(255,0,0,0.6);
				position: absolute;
			}
			p{
				width: 80%;
				margin-left: 10%;
				text-align: center;
				color: white;
				font-size: 26px;
			}
			h1{
				position: absolute;
				text-align: center;
				color: white;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				font-size: 50px;
			}
      h2{
				position: relative;
				text-align: center;
				color: white;
				width: 100%;
				font-size: 35px;
			}
			button{
				font-size: 23px;
				background-color: white;
				border: 0;
				padding: 15px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				display: inherit;
			}
      #header{
        height: 25%;
        position: relative;
      }
      #cuerpo{
        position: relative;
      }
      #footer{
        height: 10%;
        position: relative;
      }

      .card {
          box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
          max-width: 300px;
          margin: auto;
          text-align: center;
          float: left;
          background-color: orange;
          padding: 1%;
          border: 1px solid aliceblue;
      }

      .title {
          color: grey;
          font-size: 18px;
      }

      .row::after {
          content: "";
          display: table;
          clear: both;
      }
      .subtitle {
          color: black;
          font-size: 16px;
      }
      img{
        max-width: 300px;
        max-height: 200px;
      }
    </style>
    <!--[if (gte mso 9)|(IE)]>
    <style type="text/css">
        table {border-collapse: collapse !important;}
    </style>
    <![endif]-->
</head>
<body>
  <div id="header">
		<h1>lastMinuteMeal</h1>
  </div>
  <div id="cuerpo">
		<h2>El aquí y el ahora</h2>
    <p>Estas cansado yendo de establecimiento en establecimiento buscando un lugar donde comer?</p>
    <p>Tranquilo! Nosotros lo hacemos por ti!</p>

    <div class="row" style="display: flex; padding: 3%;">

      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://www.allaboutstalbans.com/media/uploaded_images/knife-and-fork-image_1.jpg">
        <h3>Fácil y rápido</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/5317/food-salad-restaurant-person.jpg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=750&w=1260">
        <h3>LLegar y comer</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/905336/pexels-photo-905336.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=750&w=1260">
        <h3>Grupos y familiares</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1080858/pexels-photo-1080858.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=750&w=1260">
        <h3>Comparte y valora</h3>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="footer">
		<p style="font-size: 14px; text-align: right;">&copy;lastMinuteMeal 2018</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
